Package com.google.publicalerts.cap.profile

This package contains classes that handle specific CAP profiles, which specify a set of extra constraints on the CAP format.

Package com.google.publicalerts.cap.profile Description

This package contains classes that handle specific CAP profiles, which specify a set of extra constraints on the CAP format. The constraints are usually country-specific.
